      "x": 767.962996187486,
      "y": 163.31610226508184,
      "width": 607.1991577148438,
      "height": 480,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 637798190,
      "version": 245,
      "versionNonce": 1522844018,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773495572960,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "n = len(nums)\n\nfor j in range(len(nums)):    => n times\n\nif nums[j] != 0                => O(1)\nnums[i] = nums[j]              => O(1)\ni += 1                         => O(1)\n\n           O(n)\n\nfor k in range(i, len(nums)):\n    nums[k] = 0\n\ni is now the number of non-zero elements moved.\n\nNumber of iterations = n - i: \nthis is exactly the number of positions remaining to fill with zeros\n\nEach assignment nums[k] = 0 is O(1)\n\nAll elements are non-zero → i = n → loop does not execute → time O(0)\nAll elements are zero → i = 0 → loop executes n times → time O(n)\n\n         O(n)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "n = len(nums)\n\nfor j in range(len(nums)):    => n times\n\nif nums[j] != 0                => O(1)\nnums[i] = nums[j]              => O(1)\ni += 1                         => O(1)\n\n           O(n)\n\nfor k in range(i, len(nums)):\n    nums[k] = 0\n\ni is now the number of non-zero elements moved.\n\nNumber of iterations = n - i: \nthis is exactly the number of positions remaining to fill with zeros\n\nEach assignment nums[k] = 0 is O(1)\n\nAll elements are non-zero → i = n → loop does not execute → time O(0)\nAll elements are zero → i = 0 → loop executes n times → time O(n)\n\n         O(n)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "RIrpK9hRqesAaheeap69W",
      "type": "text",
